Spectacular views, on the other hand, offer many heated outdoor swimming pools in Switzerland and Austria: While you can watch the entire city from the Zurich rooftop bath, you can look at the snowy Arlberg in the outdoor pool of a bath in St. Anton - and: In the steam bath there is a window from which you can observe driving on the ski slope.
