For your Costa Rican fans, a dream comes true when Pearl Jam plays in Costa Rica: Are you aware of what this means for your fans?
Playing in Costa Rica is a dream that comes true for us too.
This is just the second time we’ve been playing in South and Central America, and so far it’s been great.
